perl-extutils-cbuilder: perl-extutils-cbuilder (Compile and link C code for Perl modules)
perl-extutils-cbuilder:
perl-extutils-cbuilder: This module can build the C portions of Perl modules by invoking the
perl-extutils-cbuilder: appropriate compilers and linkers in a cross-platform manner. It was
perl-extutils-cbuilder: motivated by the Module::Build project, but may be useful for other
perl-extutils-cbuilder: purposes as well.
perl-extutils-cbuilder:
perl-extutils-cbuilder: http://search.cpan.org/dist/ExtUtils-CBuilder/
perl-extutils-cbuilder:
perl-extutils-cbuilder:
perl-extutils-cbuilder: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
